item.title: Wiki
item.description: Welcome to the Wiki! # Embark on a journey of cosmic exploration with the Wheel of Heaven Wiki. This comprehensive resource dives deep into the intriguing hypothesis that our Earth and its life forms were intricately designed by the enigmatic Elohim, a purported extraterrestrial civilization. Our wiki pages provide a detailed exploration of this fascinating narrative, blending scientific analysis with ancient wisdom, offering a unique perspective on our origins and destiny in the universe.
